Tense	Usage	Example Sentence
Present Simple	Habit, fact	She writes emails daily.
Present Continuous	Ongoing action	She is writing an email.
Past Simple	Completed action	She wrote an email yesterday.
Past Continuous	Past action in progress	She was writing an email when I called.
Future Simple	Future plan/promise	She will write an email tomorrow.
Future Continuous	Ongoing future action	She will be writing an email at 5 PM.
